title: Will Eisner: John Law - Detective
description:
The Will Eisner comic you never hear about!?!

"Here's a very fun oddity. In 1948 Will Eisner created a new detective hero: John Law. He completed a comic book's worth of material but never found a home for it. And so, save for a few bits cannibalized for The Spirit, it stayed in a drawer until the 1980s, when it was dusted off, beautifully colored, and published by Eclipse. This is that 1983 edition, ready to leap into your hands."
